title: Week 2 Studs & Duds + General Mills - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/20
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the Week 2 action! Plus, an outlook for Week 3 and the rest of the season. Which fantasy football busts so far are the most worrisome? Plus, lots of injury news and “Monday Punday!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 20th, 2021.
  
 (04:50) - Monday Punday
 (07:05) - NFL News
 (22:45) - Week 2 Studmuffins
 (23:20) - QB Studs
 (29:35) - RB Studs
 (35:35) - WR Studs
 (49:00) - TE Studs
 (50:25) - Week 2 Duds
 (50:40) - QB Duds
 (52:15) - RB Duds
